nections do, esp in sensory ctx?Our data say: they do dynamics/time.&lt;br/&gt;1/4&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/112/076/962/293/394/862/original/4970ba354431a25b.png"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/112/076/962/293/394/862/original/4970ba354431a25b.png" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">112083226511966707</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:38:30 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Boris Barbour</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@BorisBarbour/112084374799742842</link><description>&lt;a href="https://pluralistic.net/2024/03/12/market-failure/#car-wars" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;pluralistic.net/2024/03/12/mar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;ket-failure/#car-wars&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">112084374799742842</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:30:32 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Earl K. Miller</title><link>https://fediscience.org/@ekmiller/112084415484296347</link><description>A Traveling Waves Perspective on Temporal Binding&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://direct.mit.edu/jocn/article/36/4/721/115974/A-Traveling-Waves-Perspective-on-Temporal-Binding" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;direct.mit.edu/jocn/article/36&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;/4/721/115974/A-Traveling-Waves-Perspective-on-Temporal-Binding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://fediscience.org/tags/neuroscience" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;neuroscience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">112084415571107633</guid><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:40:53 +0000</pubDate></item><ite